title: Publications
aka: Publications From the Harvard Graduate School of Engineering
additional-note: Issues of this serial have distinctive titles, and were often reprinted from other publications.  Before concluding an issue is in the public domain, search for renewals for an issue under its distinctive title, and also search for renewals for the publication the contents first appeared in, if any. We have not systematically checked issue titles for this serial, but the open issues at HathiTrust have been checked.
acknowledgement: Thanks to Kristina Eden Hall for copyright research on this title.
